{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">From the developers of <i>Cris Tales</i> comes <i><strong>Prisma</strong></i>, a single-player, turn-based JRPG that blends vibrant visuals with innovative gameplay mechanics built around Alma's camera, a device that can reshape the very fabric of her world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Step into the shoes of Alma, a <strong>young photojournalist</strong> whose life takes an extraordinary twist when her camera is replaced by a mysterious device infused with prism shards. This enigmatic tool plunges her into an alternate dimension brimming with danger, thrilling adventures, and countless versions of herself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Title_Test.png?t=1733930516\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/FishEyeEffect.gif?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Inspired by the innovative mechanics of <i>Persona 5</i> and <i>The World Ends With You</i>, <strong><i>Prisma</i> blends strategy and dynamism in unique battles that harness the power of the camera's lenses.</strong> Alma\u2019s prism-enhanced camera lets you <strong>shift perspectives, curve attack trajectories, and uncover new strategies on the battlefield.</strong> Experience a one of a kind <strong>JRPG</strong> where <strong>every lens unlocks unexpected possibilities!</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the <strong>Fish-Eye Lens</strong> to curve attacks, striking enemies hidden behind front lines.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Winter_FishEye.gif?t=1733930516\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or use the <strong>Shattered Lens</strong> to divide your strikes and hit multiple enemies at once.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Shaman_Shattered.gif?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Title_Test2.png?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Island_Transition.gif?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a <strong>modern world where the unexpected is woven into daily life.</strong> As you journey through Domacon, you'll face enemies corrupted by the prism, some of which open portals that twist the world's appearance and functions.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/DockShot.gif?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage with colorful characters and vibrant environments, forging alliances, encountering enemies, and unlocking quests as you go deeper into this ever-changing world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Title_Test3.png?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your main rivals are <strong>other Almas</strong>, each shaped by their unique choices and perspectives, all trying to steal your Prism Shards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2850910/extras/Prisma_Shaman_GIF3.gif?t=1733930516\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https: